  "id": "RAW_06ca6996",
  "title": "AAAI 2026 Oral｜LENS：基于统一强化推理的分割大模型",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651009577&idx=4&sn=b0c849752ea5d8695da2a267504d605a",
  "date": "2025-12-29 04:42:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">文本提示图像分割（Text-prompted image segmentation）是实现精细化视觉理解的关键技术，在人机交互、具身智能及机器人等前沿领域具有重大的战略意义。这项技术使机器能够根据自然语言指令，在复杂的视觉场景中定位并分割出任意目标。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">然而，当前主流的技术路径，如基于监督式微调（Supervised Fine-Tuning, SFT）的方法，正面临着根本性的瓶颈。这些方法本质上是静态的模式匹配，虽然在特定数据集上表现优异，但其泛化能力往往受限，形成了一个难以逾越的 “能力天花板”。尤其是在处理需要多步、复杂推理的未知指令时，性能会显著下降，其根源在于 SFT 方法在训练中忽略了动态的、显式的推理过程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了 shatter 这一能力天花板，我们引入了 LENS（Learning to Segment Anything with Unified Reinforced Reasoning）框架。LENS 摒弃了静态的 SFT，转而采用端到端的强化学习（Reinforcement Learning, RL）机制，将高层次的 “思考” 过程（即思维链推理）与像素级的 “执行” 过程（即图像分割）进行动态的联合优化。通过这种设计，LENS 旨在赋予分割模型真正的、上下文感知的推理能力，从而在根本上提升其在复杂任务中的鲁棒性和泛化性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本文将深入介绍一下我们 AAAI 荣获 Oral 的工作，“会思考的分割大模型 LENS”。有幸在这次 AAAI 2026 得到了审稿人们一致正面的评价，并被 AC 和 PC 一致同意推荐为 Oral 论文。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503525284\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.18796296296296297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7ed9bbb6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZTOULeibJSu4mkiaFwAXGe2otZvv2sYRLHpO39xfACRicPA8zOW4h3Vl0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文标题：LENS: Learning to Segment Anything with Unified Reinforced Reasoning &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文链接：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.14153\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.14153</a> &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">代码链接：<a href=\"https://github.com/hustvl/LENS\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hustvl/LENS</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">LENS 框架概览：推理与分割的协同进化</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在这个工作中，我们研究了分割大模型领域的一大一小两个关键问题，大问题就是老生常谈的 “泛化能力”，传统分割大模型对未见过的提示和领域的泛化能力往往有限；小问题则是隐藏的 “信息瓶颈”，此前的分割大模型从 “大脑思考”（MLLM）到 “分割解码”（SAM）之间往往只通过单一的分割 Token 传递信息，存在隐形的 “信息输送瓶颈”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503525285\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8740740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 447px;height: 391px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7844b4e0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZ0OBwEic5ey0xJcPKd1PxH0mia3njjUrzCSIuD8IGKPopGnsx4vic5F6QA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">LENS 框架的核心设计在于通过端到端的联合优化，彻底打破传统模型中 “思考”（推理）与 “执行”（分割）之间的信息壁垒。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以往的方法，例如同期的优秀工作 Seg-Zero，采用的是非端到端的设计，即先由推理模型生成边界框和点提示，再交由现成的（off-the-shelf）SAM 进行分割。这种分离式流程的主要缺陷在于误差的单向传播。这意味着像 Seg-Zero 这样的非端到端模型是根本上脆弱的；它们的性能上限被其初始猜测的准确性所锁定。一旦推理阶段的定位出现偏差，下游的分割模型将无法纠正，最终必然导致分割失败。相比之下，LENS 通过其端到端的反馈闭环，具备了即便从不完美的初步定位中也能自我纠正的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503525286\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7046296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e95e680&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZT2ialTkwibUWzhbfFRNsWC2iaBTomLEkpzr65G3kq7x9QenLfcEn2LRSQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">LENS 的整体架构由三大核心组件构成，它们协同工作，实现了从高级语义理解到精确像素输出的无缝衔接：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">多模态大语言模型 (MLLM) - 推理核心</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：作为系统的 “大脑”，LENS 采用先进的 MLLM（如 Qwen2.5-VL-3B-Instruct）来处理输入的图像和文本指令。它负责生成详尽的思维链（Chain-of-Thought, CoT）推理过程，并给出一个初步的目标边界框。这一过程不仅是定位，更是对指令的深度理解。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们将系统提示&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503525287\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"60\" style=\"width: 46px;height: 25px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd24af79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZ53Y3r7adoEIYVAKj6FXIh3lgibwOicuNpYGDSiaNEmmBfc96DWe41Xhdw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、文本指令 T 以及图像 I 输入到 MLLM 推理模型&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503525288\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.40476190476190477\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"84\" style=\"width: 70px;height: 28px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=caa97ed2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZB5g2S1SKanesdcqcGlDsrHCeDVBBIibEgVYf1ibtn82OH6TTWJG6DhEA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;中，得到思维链（COT）&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503525290\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5753424657534246\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"73\" style=\"width: 49px;height: 28px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eef1ef1c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZRicOCBmaKyFVZ0XQD01XYTBRzOic4TTow3Xwo7sF4aDt7SnYEevDf3EQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;和边界框预测&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503525292\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5909090909090909\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"66\" style=\"width: 40px;height: 24px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c27e91ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZoic9kFfj5SIrDkJoVagjQAor9558iaJVUSC6xKEsRaicxjeGWY3Pic0b1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503525304\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.0920353982300885\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"565\" style=\"width: 368px;height: 34px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a73099be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZwNFYxfCs18Xagse22R4UfDErN3QUf4JaaJMPZQH8tBV1loXtuibgXicg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">上下文模块 (Context Module) - 信息桥梁</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：这是 LENS 的关键创新，它充当了 MLLM 和分割模型之间的信息高速公路。该模块由一组可学习的上下文查询（Context Queries）和一个连接器（Connector）组成，其任务是将 MLLM 生成的丰富推理轨迹和定位信息，转化为分割模型能够高效利用的、信息密集的分割提示。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们随机初始化上下文查询&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503525307\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.2792207792207792\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"154\" style=\"width: 106px;height: 30px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c907aafd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZicSRibOyoetlYq0HHicephO0zlh5w4Z3UYibRbM7ic7XPjWriciaynib2rlsEQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，其中 M 表示上下文查询的数量，C 表示多模态大语言模型（MLLM）的隐藏维度。 需要注意的是，上下文查询被追加到输入序列和生成序列的末尾，并通过一次前向传播来汇聚信息。随后，我们将 MLLM 输出的上下文查询嵌入&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503525309\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.24848484848484848\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"165\" style=\"width: 118px;height: 29px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d1e9f3ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZ3HGJjrYAEnTLWxQCqTJM0G4y2tnCb9ib8PzOrQBibvJQnacQiaxPywXXA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;输入到连接器（connector）中。该连接器是一个浅层 Transformer，用于将上下文查询嵌入投影到 SAM 的提示空间中，即&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503525312\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6190476190476191\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"63\" style=\"width: 45px;height: 28px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e616dd6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZwd1HNm3nbFAoH2VfOweoxvNLGt9SLU0g6bqj2UIU02VudFEpAmkZyA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503525316\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.1312\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"625\" style=\"width: 420px;height: 55px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=47a3390d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZpgN191w1Su3OLTIYRlIHkoibxUqnJDyPSiaD0xz6KicQyNlByDsnXswRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">分割模型 (SAM-2) - 像素解码器：作为系统的 “双手”，LENS 采用高性能的分割模型（SAM2-Large）。它接收来自上下文模块的复杂指令，并结合原始图像信息，执行精准的像素级掩码生成任务，将推理结果精确地体现在图像上。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503525325\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.17132867132867133\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"286\" style=\"width: 206px;height: 35px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3ebff367&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZdznl9k7fqOl9aBz82suI72yH447hSuP7uOl5dKzPgqpibP9m6frqALQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过这种 “推理 - 桥接 - 分割” 三位一体的紧密耦合架构，LENS 实现了推理质量和分割精度的同步提升。这种设计使得最终的分割性能可以直接反作用于推理过程的优化，形成一个完整的闭环，为实现更高水平的通用分割能力奠定了基础。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">LENS 框架同时在 “思考推理” 端也做出了改进，我们基于 Group Relative Policy Optimization（GRPO）方法构建了统一强化学习奖励机制（Unified Rewards Scheme）。该奖励机制是多维度的，同时监督以下三个层级的线索：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">格式奖励（Format Reward）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：确保 MLLM 的输出（包括推理过程和定位结果）遵循预期的结构和格式一致性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">边界框 IoU 奖励（Box IoU Reward）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：衡量预测边界框与真实边界框之间的定位准确性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">分割掩码 IoU 奖励（Segment IoU Reward）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：评估像素级分割掩码的质量。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503525327\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3861111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=96c1db10&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZuiaMP9b7XG9d30PibzZBCIcettLkdnW9V8uHSs1c94Ee3tDsUglSJtPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过我们提出的联合优化（将统一的 GRPO 目标与监督分割损失相结合），LENS 能够从奖励驱动的推理改进和直接的分割监督中同时受益。值得一提的是，LENS 的端到端特性解决了定位错误（Grounding Error）向下游传播的问题，如上图右一右二所示，哪怕有些情况定位框是错的，强大的上下文查询（Context Query）也能带领分割模型走向正确。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">性能评估与分析</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503525328\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5101851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4079592a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZGZNjGJCA1RyczgPjjuDNGvn4ZnxqXNRcvft1nPibkLRqaM8FytVELIA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">核心结果方面，LENS 取得了文本提示分割任务的最先进性能（SoTA）：LENS 在 RefCOCO 系列的基准测试中取得了 81.2% 的平均 cIoU，达到了世界最高水平。在 GroundingSuite-Eval 这类更具挑战性的零样本基准测试中，LENS 展现出卓越的域外泛化能力，cIoU 达到 78.3%，超越第二优方法接近 10%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503525331\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3037037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cf79d123&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW98iacuWAiaBTm2Iq243SoVCZfRqIdibkvMj0oZVbFLNbFhiasLrUSwFrukporiaBBEqsRL2mpqcYCuObg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这些成果表明，LENS 这一类基于统一强化学习奖励驱动的 CoT 推理方法，能够显著提升文本提示下的分割能力。我们相信，LENS 为强化学习与视觉分割的无缝集成提供了新的思路，并有望推动更通用、更稳健的视觉 - 语言系统的研究。代码和预训练权重已开源（<a href=\"https://github.com/hustvl/LENS），感兴趣的朋友们欢迎研究和使用。我们也期待在\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hustvl/LENS），感兴趣的朋友们欢迎研究和使用。我们也期待在</a> AAAI 2026 与学术界同行进行深入交流。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "LENS 框架通过强化学习统一推理和分割过程，解决了传统分割模型泛化能力和信息瓶颈问题，实现了文本提示图像分割的显著性能提升，并在 AAAI 2026 荣获 Oral 论文。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "LENS 框架通过强化学习统一推理和分割过程，解决了传统分割模型泛化能力和信息瓶颈问题，实现了文本提示图像分割的显著性能提升，并在 AAAI 2026 荣获 Oral 论文。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了 AAAI 2026 Oral 论文 \"LENS: Learning to Segment Anything with Unified Reinforced Reasoning\"。该研究针对当前文本提示图像分割技术（如基于 SFT 的方法）在处理复杂指令和泛化能力上的瓶颈，提出 LENS 框架。LENS 核心在于摒弃静态 SFT，采用端到端强化学习机制，将高层次的“思考”过程（思维链推理）与像素级的“执行”过程（图像分割）进行动态联合优化。框架由多模态大语言模型（MLLM）作为推理核心，上下文模块作为信息桥梁连接 MLLM 输出与分割模型，以及 SAM-2 作为像素解码器组成。LENS 创新性地构建了统一强化学习奖励机制（包含格式、边界框 IoU 和分割掩码 IoU 奖励），并通过联合优化解决了传统方法中误差单向传播的问题，使得模型在不完美的初步定位下也能自我纠正。实验结果表明，LENS 在 RefCOCO 系列基准测试中达到了 SOTA 性能，并在零样本 GroundingSuite-Eval 测试中展现出卓越的域外泛化能力，远超现有方法。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "LENS 框架通过端到端强化学习机制整合思维链推理与图像分割。",
      "explanation": "LENS 彻底改变了传统的静态监督式微调方法，采用强化学习将高层次的语言理解和低层次的像素操作进行动态联合优化，从而赋予模型更强的泛化能力和对复杂指令的理解力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "LENS 解决了传统模型中“思考”与“执行”之间的信息壁垒和误差传播问题。",
      "explanation": "通过多模态大语言模型、上下文模块和分割模型的紧密耦合，LENS 实现了信息高效传递，并通过反馈闭环，支持模型在初步定位不精确时也能进行自我纠正，避免了误差的累积传播。"
    },
    {
      "point": "引入了多维度的统一强化学习奖励机制以优化推理过程。",
      "explanation": "LENS 的奖励机制涵盖格式、边界框 IoU 和分割掩码 IoU，这使得模型不仅仅是在像素层面学习，更在推理和定位层面获得监督，从而实现推理质量和分割精度的双重提升。"
    },
    {
      "point": "LENS 在多项基准测试中取得了当前最佳性能，特别是零样本泛化能力强。",
      "explanation": "LENS 在 RefCOCO 和 GroundingSuite-Eval 等关键数据集上均超越了现有 SOTA 方法，尤其在域外泛化能力方面表现突出，证明了其在解决复杂视觉理解任务上的优越性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "用强化学习，将高层次的 \"思考\" 过程与像素级的 \"执行\" 过程进行动态联合优化。",
    "LENS 摒弃了静态的 SFT，转而采用端到端的强化学习（Reinforcement Learning， RL）机制，将高层次的 \"思考\" 过程（即思维链推理）与像素级的 \"执行\" 过程（即图像分割）进行动态的联合优化。",
    "LENS 通过其端到端的反馈闭环，具备了即便从不完美的初步定位中也能自我纠正的能力。",
    "LENS 能够从奖励驱动的推理改进和直接的分割监督中同时受益。",
    "LENS 在 RefCOCO 系列的基准测试中取得了 81.2% 的平均 cIoU，达到了世界最高水平。"
  ],
